data.title: No Poverty
data.description: End poverty in all its forms everywhere

data.description: Make cities and human settlements inclusive, safe, resilient and sustainable

data.description: Ensure sustainable consumption and production patterns

data.title: Life Below Water
data.description: Conserve and sustainably use the oceans, seas and marine resources for sustainable development

data.title: Life on Land
data.description: Protect, restore and promote sustainable use of terrestrial ecosystems, sustainably manage forests, combat desertification, and halt and reverse land degradation and halt biodiversity loss
